== Polk's Declaration of War ==

Could someone list all the congressmen who made up the Immortal Fourteen who voted no to the bill declaring war against Mexico in 1847? Also can someone find me an online copy of this bill with its controversial preamble? Also did Calhoun abstain from the vote and if so who else abstained?--[[Special:Contributions/170.140.105.10|170.140.105.10]] ([[User talk:170.140.105.10|talk]]) 00:30, 23 April 2014 (UTC)
:"[[Immortal Fourteen]]"? ←[[User:Baseball Bugs|Baseball Bugs]] <sup>''[[User talk:Baseball Bugs|What's up, Doc?]]''</sup> [[Special:Contributions/Baseball_Bugs|carrots]]→ 00:45, 23 April 2014 (UTC)
