:::The full text of the Act and the preamble are here (scroll down to where it says Chapter 16). [http://books.google.ca/books?id=nJhAAAAAYAAJ&pg=PA367&lpg=PA367&dq=29th+congress+1st+session+mexico+chapter+16&source=bl&ots=JTjh6-ANFp&sig=nErZFxl0VWkwpCzCAYERPFWpSdI&hl=en&sa=X&ei=2RNXU4P6B-jC2wWIkYDADw&ved=0CCoQ6AEwAA] [[User:OttawaAC|OttawaAC]] ([[User talk:OttawaAC|talk]]) 01:17, 23 April 2014 (UTC)

